@startuml
title UC10 - Enviar Moedas de Mérito

' Configuração visual melhorada
hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #374151
    LifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
    ActorBorderColor #374151
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    DatabaseBorderColor #374151
    DatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
    BoxBorderColor #9CA3AF
    BoxBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    GroupBorderColor #9CA3AF
    GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ActivationBorderColor #111827
    ActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
    ParticipantPadding 28
    BoxPadding 10
    MessageAlign center
}
skinparam maxMessageSize 70

actor Professor as P
boundary "Painel do Professor
Next.js" as Front
control "TransacaoController
Micronaut" as Ctrl
control "ProfessorRepository" as ProfRepo
control "AlunoRepository" as AlunoRepo
control "TransacaoRepository" as TransRepo
queue "RabbitMQ
moedas.email" as MQ
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

P -> Front: Informa aluno, valor e motivo
activate Front
note right of Front
  Valida campos, valor positivo
  e saldo disponível do professor.
end note
Front -> Ctrl: POST /transacoes
CriarTransacaoRequest
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> ProfRepo: findById(remetenteId)
activate ProfRepo
ProfRepo -> DB: SELECT professor
activate DB
DB --> ProfRepo: Professor
deactivate DB
ProfRepo --> Ctrl: Professor
deactivate ProfRepo

Ctrl -> AlunoRepo: findById(destinatarioId)
activate AlunoRepo
AlunoRepo -> DB: SELECT aluno
activate DB
DB --> AlunoRepo: Aluno
deactivate DB
AlunoRepo --> Ctrl: Aluno
deactivate AlunoRepo

note right of Ctrl
  Verifica saldo, curso e instituição.
  Em seguida atualiza saldos.
end note

Ctrl -> ProfRepo: update(professor)
activate ProfRepo
ProfRepo -> DB: UPDATE saldo_corrente
activate DB
DB --> ProfRepo: OK
deactivate DB
ProfRepo --> Ctrl: Professor atualizado
deactivate ProfRepo

Ctrl -> AlunoRepo: update(aluno)
activate AlunoRepo
AlunoRepo -> DB: UPDATE saldo_atual
activate DB
DB --> AlunoRepo: OK
deactivate DB
AlunoRepo --> Ctrl: Aluno atualizado
deactivate AlunoRepo

Ctrl -> TransRepo: save(transacao)
activate TransRepo
TransRepo -> DB: INSERT transacao
activate DB
DB --> TransRepo: Transação salva
deactivate DB
TransRepo --> Ctrl: Transação
deactivate TransRepo

Ctrl -> MQ: Publica EnvioMoedasEvent
activate MQ
MQ --> Ctrl: Mensagem aceita
deactivate MQ
Ctrl --> Front: 201 Created
StatusResponse
deactivate Ctrl
Front -> Front: Recarrega saldo e histórico
Front --> P: Toast de sucesso
deactivate Front
@enduml
